App Updates
We will, from time to time, update the SayIt app, in order to improve its functionality or make it available for new versions of Android or iOS as these are released.
Whilst we try to ensure these updates retain functionality on older devices, we recognise that there are circumstances beyond our control, such as changes to the Android and iOS operating systems, to which the SayIt app must conform.
We cannot guarantee that future updates of the SayIt app will continue to function on older devices, especially those running obsolete versions of the Android or iOS operating systems, or which have been "rooted" or "jailbroken" so as to alter their security model from that provided by the manufacturer.
In purchasing and using the app you accept that this is an acceptable risk and that we will not refund your purchase price should the app cease to function because of circumstances outside our control, explicitly because of Android or iOS updates.
